data.title: Tactics: Seoul Dynasty Clutches a 3v6 with less than 10 Seconds Left
data.description: No matter how one-sided an Overwatch teamfight is looking, it's truly never over until it's actually over. In this episode of Tactics, we review an Overtime teamfight that the Seoul Dynasty miraculously clutched vs. the Chengdu Hunters when they were at a massive numbers disadvantage with only seconds left in their time bank. data.title: My Hero: Ana
data.description: Ana's one of the most mechanically-demanding healers and a top pick for Overwatch League support players! Hear from Seoul Dynasty's ryujehong, New York Excelsior's JJoNak, Vancouver Titans' Twilight, and Paris Eternal's Greyy as they break down her high-utility kit and teach you how to get max value from Overwatch's veteran support sniper.
